vernac_cmds: Definition bool_eq (a a':bool) : Prop := a = a'.
Definition ascii_eq (a a':ascii) : Prop := a = a'.
Definition string_eq (a a':string) : Prop := a = a'.
Lemma string_assoc : forall s s' s'':string, ((s ++ s') ++ s'')%string = (s ++ (s' ++ s''))%string.
Fixpoint str_length (s:string) : nat := match s with | ""%string => O | String _ s' => S (str_length s') end.
Lemma str_length_append : forall s s', str_length (s ++ s')%string = str_length s + str_length s'.
Definition bneq_empty_string(s:string):bool := match (string_dec s ""%string) with | left _ => false | right _ => true end.
Definition concat_list_string(xs:list string) := fold_right (fun s s' : string => (s ++ s')%string) ""%string xs.
Lemma concat_list_string_x_xs : forall (x:string)(xs:list string), concat_list_string (x :: xs) = (x ++ (concat_list_string xs))%string.
Lemma concat_list_string_xs_x : forall (xs:list string)(x:string), concat_list_string (xs ++ x::nil) = ((concat_list_string xs) ++ x)%string.
Lemma In_list_append_left : forall A (a:A) l l', In a l -> In a (l ++ l')%list.
Lemma In_list_append_right : forall A (a:A) l l', In a l' -> In a (l ++ l')%list.
Lemma In_snoc : forall A (a:A) l, In a (l ++ a::nil)%list.
Lemma forallb_divide_left : forall (A:Type)(f:A -> bool) (l l':list A), forallb f (l ++ l') = true -> forallb f l = true.
intros A f l l' H.
destruct(forallb f l'); simpl in H; discriminate H.
Lemma forallb_divide_right : forall (A:Type)(f:A -> bool) (l l':list A), forallb f (l ++ l') = true -> forallb f l' = true.
intros A f l l' H.
destruct(forallb f l); simpl in H; discriminate H.
Lemma forallb_list_x_xs : forall A (f:A -> bool)(x:A)(xs:list A), f x = true -> forallb f xs = true -> forallb f (x::xs) = true.
intros A f x xs Hx Hxs.
Lemma forallb_list_xs_x : forall A (f:A -> bool)(xs:list A)(x:A), forallb f xs = true -> f x = true -> forallb f (xs ++ x::nil)%list = true.
intros A f xs x Hxs Hx.

command: intros A f l l' H.
destruct(forallb f l'); simpl in H; discriminate H.
intros A f l l' H.
destruct(forallb f l); simpl in H; discriminate H.
intros A f x xs Hx Hxs.
intros A f xs x Hxs Hx.
